body_html:
Looks like android-support-v4.jar is missing in the build server.
Is it possible to install the android-support-v4.jar in the server?

If not, I can inline the ContextCompat (which requires android-support-v4.jar) like the way I did for v13 support library.

Looks like android-support-v4.jar is missing in the build server.
Is it possible to install the android-support-v4.jar in the server?

If not, I can inline the ContextCompat (which requires android-support-v4.jar) like the way I did for v13 support library.
